ygData.messageBody:
OOh OOOh... okay, I made a fixer on Rubi-Ka 2 but was surprised there were
never any other players on. She's only 2 and I'm sure I screwed everything up
so I'll probably restart her. Clan, name Iceiallana (surprise there :-). I
tried a Doctor on Rubi-Ka 1 last night, Omni-Tek Nano-human thingy. Died in
my first mission but still figuring it out (think I got the program thingies
down, but I right clicked something in my inventory by accident and it went
away so I'll probably restart her too. Her name is Caedusia (favorite cleric
name).

So those were my guesses based on EQ. I played a tanking druid, much to the
amusement of all my friends :-) I did love ranger when I started one, but
hated the exp. penalty. Enjoy cleric and bard. I really like the speed and
healing buffs, but I get bored if I just do the sit/med thing while the tanks
are having all the fun pulling.

Suggestions? From reading the boards I thought eventually I'd play a
meta-nanophysicist neutral. Looks like that will be a total bitch to play,
though, but what great RP :-)

Ice

I'm in Anarchy Online now and was in the beta. Yes you really can do stuff
in an hour. But - grouping probably isn't it, solo missions are great for
that time frame. You also lose "chat" in solo missions at level 6 - and it
makes for a very lonely time after (high player turnover rate now too).

I do like it though. I'm mainly on first dimension now since the second is
sooo empty during the day when I play. Let me know who you are I'll send
you a tell ;0 And if you describe your playstyle I can give you a list of
classes to fit.

Lora / Hechicera on boards

Gonna try enchanter... Luna, HELP!

Ice
